Trinity:;

She rubbed her eyes with her paws and continued to cry.  She was 
scared of these new bots and didn't know what to think or do.  But 
she was also upset over the loss of her whole family.  All she could 
do was cry.  She looked up at Archangle and Kol with uncertainty and 
fear.
